data.text: STAR DISCOVERED BY MICHAEL MCNAMARA EPOC 6011:663.457
A SMALL, WEAK, COLD, BROWN DWARF STAR. WHAT MORE CAN I SAY

ADDITION TO NOTE, GOOD PLACE TO FUEL UP.
